{
  "stem": "8962.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Everybody brought something because you didn't have much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And what happened one day-- we're coming, but he was gone.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They had picked him up again, without his crutches, without his canes, and we never heard from him again.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They had shipped him to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That, they told us, told his parents.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But nobody ever saw him again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "In the meantime, my uncle, my father's only remaining brother, was arrested and was shipped to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And the tortures he had to go through were indescribable, like putting a hose down his throat and turning on the water and standing out in the cold without shoes and socks.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They took away the clothes, of course, and they were wearing those pajama-type things, all in the freezing cold.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was all interrupted by Crystal Night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother and I and this old man that lived with us were in the apartment, and I got up in the morning to go to work.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I get on a streetcar, and I see people moving away from me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I see a truck going by the streetcar and men standing in them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, what in the hell is this?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Where are they going in a truck?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, oh, my God, they have beards and hats on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They're Jews, truckloads full of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had arrested all the men and women and brought them to a place called the [NON-ENGLISH], where operas would be played and music would be played, and lectures-- and they made the-- they brought out scissors, and they cut off the beards of the religious people who wore beards because of religion, not because they liked it.",
      "word_count": 58
    }
  ],
